---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>{tagline}</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f9fafb;
        color: #111;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      header, section, footer {
        padding: 4rem 2rem;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        text-align: center;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      h2 {
        font-size: 1.75rem;
        margin-top: 3rem;
      }
      .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        background: #0070f3;
        color: white;
        padding: 1rem 2rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
        transition: background 0.3s;
        margin-top: 1rem;
      }
      .cta-button:hover {
        background: #005bb5;
      }
      ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        text-align: left;
      }
      li {
        margin: 1rem 0;
      }
      table {
        width: 100%;
        margin-top: 2rem;
        border-collapse: collapse;
      }
      td, th {
        padding: 0.75rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;
        text-align: left;
      }
      #snow {
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        pointer-events: none;
        z-index: 9999;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .snowflake {
        position: absolute;
        top: -2em;
        color: #fff;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        user-select: none;
        animation: fall linear infinite;
        opacity: 0.8;
        transform: translateX(0); /* Ensure transform starts from 0 */
      }
      @keyframes fall {
        to {
          transform: translateY(100vh) translateX(var(--drift, 0));
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="snow"></div>

    <header>
      <h1>{tagline}</h1>
      <p>{subtitle}</p>
      <a class="cta-button" href={ctaLink} target="_blank">{ctaText}</a>
    </header>

    <section>
      <h2>The Problem</h2>
      <p>Traditional foam rollers warm up after minutes. Ice packs slide off. You need pressure <strong>and</strong> cold ‚Äî and you need it to last.</p>
    </section>

